c: 34
v: 13
t: "Li ile tsa etsa tsohle tseo a neng a li laba-labela, mahlala: masinakhokhe a likereke, lifika, tsa betla likotloloana tse kang liliba le likotloloana tsa ts’epe tse ahiloeng fats’e. Fanang ka liteboho, Bara ba Davida! Ke ba fokolang feela ba makhabunyane a Ka ba fanang ka liteboho.”"